timing_allow_i...n_clock_source(25.10)  timing_allow_i...n_clock_source(25.10)

Name
       timing_allow_input_delay_on_clock_source

Syntax
        timing_allow_input_delay_on_clock_source

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When set to true, this global variable allows the software to apply in-
       put delay constraints on a pin where a clock was previously asserted.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

